Alert-Handler version 0.0.1

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	sudo make install

DEPENDENCIES

	use warnings;
	use strict;
	use Carp;
	use Safe;
	use version;
	use warnings;
	use Crypt::GPG;
	use WWW::Curl::Easy;
	use XML::Bare;
	use Email::Simple;
	use Config::IniFiles;
	
On debian based systems install:
	libcrypt-gpg-perl libwww-curl-perl libxml-bare-perl
	libemail-simple-perl liblog-dispatch-perl libdbi-perl libconfig-inifiles-perl
	libdatetime-format-strptime-perl libdatetime-format-mysql-perl

GPG INSTALLATION

In order to decrypt incoming emails setupt the private key information
in the GpgConfig.cfg.


